00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:37,760
Brother.

18
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,360
I knew you'd be here.

19
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,320
Let's watch the play.

20
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,480
All right.

21
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:16,720
- Great!
- Nice!

