00:03:20,730 --> 00:03:22,350
(Pavilion of Plays)

23
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,240
Endure hardships to make
the nation prosper.

24
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,760
A gentleman must forbear
temporary humiliation.

25
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,840
If you don't kill traitors
in the nation,

26
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,400
how can you make the nation prosper?

27
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,320
Brother.

28
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,320
I'm willing to accompany you

29
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,680
in winning this battle.

30
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:04,800
- Splendid!
- Amazing!

31
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,920
Everyone says

32
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,480
that I killed you.

33
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:29,480
I also tell myself

34
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,960
that I killed you.

35
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,440
But now,

36
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,960
someone is saying that I didn't.

37
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,760
Brother.

38
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,960
Did you hear that?

39
00:05:23,830 --> 00:05:26,690
(Prince Guang's Residence)

40
00:05:37,880 --> 00:05:38,480
Your Highness.

41
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,200
Princess Ninghe is coming back.

42
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,240
Really?

43
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,360
Definitely.

44
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,240
Could this really

45
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,200
be Ninghe's doing?

46
00:05:58,950 --> 00:06:01,450
(Report)

47
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:10,580
(Bring Princess Ninghe back to Heng'an)

48
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:12,960
You're saying

49
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:14,760
that you have Aunt Ninghe?

50
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,160
Your Highness.

51
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,640
The brave Princess Misha

52
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,760
from the Zhenwu Army

53
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,720
saved Princess Ninghe

54
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,960
(Zhenwu Region Governor, Sun Lie)
from the rebels in Lucong.

55
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:29,600
You're quite ready to act bravely
for a just cause.

56
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,600
It's the Zhenwu Army's
moral obligation

57
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,400
to bring Princess Ninghe
back to Heng'an.

58
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:39,880
Did Ninghe ask

59
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,000
to return here herself?

60
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,680
It was Princess Misha's decision.

61
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,040
Lucong is in major chaos now.

62
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:47,320
As a princess,

63
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,720
Princess Ninghe shouldn't be
wandering out there.

64
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,280
She should return to her family
in Heng'an instead.

65
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,880
They're already on the way.

66
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,160
They should be here in half a month.

67
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,440
What's the matter?

68
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,680
You don't think it's appropriate,
Duke Chu?

69
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,600
No.

70
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,240
Not only should she return,

71
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,240
she must return

72
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,000
in a grand manner.

73
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:16,880
Everyone in the imperial court

74
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,680
must welcome her outside
the palace gate.

75
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,600
Your Majesty.

76
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,640
Am I right?

77
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,520
Yes.

78
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,400
Issue the decree then.

79
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,640
Everyone.

80
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:38,680
Go outside the palace gate

81
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,960
to welcome Aunt Ninghe.

82
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,600
That includes me.

83
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,320
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

84
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,000
This won't do, Your Majesty.

85
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:55,960
Since you already know

86
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:57,160
that Princess Ninghe is the third party,

87
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,760
why are you letting her return?

88
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,520
I'm not the one
who's letting her come back.

89
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:03,880
It is Qiu Ziliang.

90
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,640
Qiu Ziliang

91
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,520
also suspects Princess Ninghe.

92
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,440
Am I right?

93
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,120
What we can find out,

94
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,600
Qiu Yanzhi can also find out.

95
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,520
Then Qiu Ziliang

96
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,000
surely doesn't have any good intentions.

97
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:30,880
What are you looking for?

98
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,799
I'm checking

99
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:34,320
about the feud between Qiu Ziliang

100
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:35,760
and Princess Ninghe.

101
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,520
There won't be any records
in the Resume.

102
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,400
Instead of looking for it there,

103
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:40,960
why don't you ask me directly?

104
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:46,840
Your Majesty, you know?

105
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,160
Even if I was still
very young back then,

106
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,920
I remember things.

107
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,440
Back then, the provincial
military commissioner

108
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,480
originally wanted to marry my Ninth Aunt.

109
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,800
But Qiu Ziliang suggested
to the late emperor

110
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,480
that Aunt Ninghe is the most
suitable candidate.

111
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,160
In the end,

112
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,880
Aunt Ninghe was the one
who married to a far place

113
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:12,360
and completed this political marriage.

114
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,560
Why?

115
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:17,840
I don't know

116
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,720
why the two of them

117
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:19,800
had a feud.

118
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,720
But Aunt Ninghe

119
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,720
said something before she left.

120
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:26,240
What was it?

121
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,680
Your Majesty.

122
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:30,880
Your Majesty!

123
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:38,720
(Princess Ninghe)
Isn't there anything you want to say to me?

124
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,120
Qiu Ziliang.

125
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:01,400
Don't be too pleased.

126
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,920
In life,

127
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,040
there's karma.

128
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,400
Someday,

129
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,520
I'll pay you back

130
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,880
for what you did to me!

131
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:18,000
I will return.

132
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,320
I'll surely return!

133
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:24,800
I know that you'll return.

134
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,800
I'll welcome you back.

135
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,240
What's the matter?

136
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:35,960
How will you return?

137
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,400
You'll return when you're dead?

138
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:49,840
There's no doubt that Princess Ninghe

139
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,520
is the third party.

140
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:52,760
First,

141
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:55,240
she told the assassin
to try to kill you,

142
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:56,920
then framed the Chess of Generals Camp
for it.

143
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,680
However, you didn't fall for the trick.

144
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,320
That was why she used

145
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,440
her second trick,

146
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,840
Wu.

147
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:05,120
She's a princess.

148
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,200
She grew up beside Empress Dowager,

149
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,080
so she has old servants in her palace.

150
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,360
That was why

151
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,440
she was able to let Wu
enter the palace smoothly.

152
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,920
The she instigated Wu

153
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,720
to assassinate Qiu Ziliang
in the banquet.

154
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:18,080
However, you didn't fall
for her trick again.

155
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:21,160
In the end, she can only
tell the assassin

156
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:23,080
to try to kill you in the Wine Shop,

157
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,800
and let Chess of Generals Camp
discover Yuzhen Hall.

158
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,800
This way, you and Qiu Ziliang

159
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:28,920
will surely be at odds.

160
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,760
However...

161
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,120
She should have waited longer.

162
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:36,880
She could have returned

163
00:11:38,640 --> 00:11:40,400
until after a winner is determined

164
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,160
between me and Qiu Ziliang,

165
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:44,160
or after we bring destruction
upon each other.

166
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:46,240
Right.

167
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:48,400
Coming back now

168
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,600
is not a wise decision.

169
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:52,240
It's obvious that Qiu Ziliang

170
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:53,480
will deal with her.

171
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,520
There are only two possibilities.

172
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,440
First.

173
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,040
There's no turning back for her anymore.

174
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,280
She doesn't know where to go,

175
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:01,960
so she can only return to Heng'an.

176
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:04,160
Because of the major chaos in Lucong?

177
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:07,200
That's the biggest possibility.

178
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,280
What's the second possibility then?

179
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:14,160
The second possibility

180
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,480
is that Aunt Ninghe
isn't the third party.

181
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,560
Just like Wu,

182
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:21,080
perhaps she was also forced to take part

183
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:23,560
in this matter

184
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,480
as a bait.

185
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:33,120
Ninghe will arrive in Heng'an
after ten days.

186
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:36,640
His Majesty and other officials

187
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,960
will personally welcome her
outside the palace gate.

188
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,040
Go and make arrangements.

189
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,800
Father, I think you said

190
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,080
that you wouldn't allow her to return.

191
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,760
If she dares to come back,

192
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:58,000
I'll dare to kill her.

193
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:00,040
While I'm at it,

194
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,640
I'll scare the imperial court
officials a bit.

195
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,080
I understand.

196
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:06,280
Yanzhi.

197
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:10,200
Do it nicely.

198
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,280
Yes.

199
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,200
Yan Xiu.

200
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:16,920
What is His Majesty busy with
in the past few days?

201
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:17,840
Sir.

202
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,840
After bringing Little Fish back
to the palace,

203
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:21,000
he never went out again.

204
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,040
During his free time,

205
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,040
he's been practicing the bow
and arrow with Little Fish.

206
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:27,080
Little Fish?

207
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:27,680
Little...

208
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:29,520
Cheng Ruoyu.

209
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:33,360
It seems like

210
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,480
His Majesty really wants to train her.

211
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:41,480
Is Prince An back?

212
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,400
We already picked him up
from his mother's maternal family.

213
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,520
They said

214
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:45,400
that as long as you

215
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:46,920
are willing to let Prince An become
the heir apparent,

216
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,200
they're willing to obey you.

217
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,560
Bring him over.

218
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:53,720
Yes.

219
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:02,280
Father.

220
00:14:03,120 --> 00:14:04,760
Qi Yan values Cheng Ruoyu.

221
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,680
Will she become an obstacle for us?

222
00:14:08,640 --> 00:14:10,800
Cheng Ruoyu is all brawn and no brain.

223
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,680
She's nothing to worry about.

224
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,800
It's just that Qi Yan...

225
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:22,600
I was wrong about him back then.

226
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,680
Qi Yan is very ambitious.

227
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:27,360
It's unavoidable

228
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:28,600
to be careless, Father.

229
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:37,320
Zhi'er.

230
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:41,400
Have you witnessed

231
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,320
His Majesty's martial arts skill?

232
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:44,880
Not yet.

233
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:47,960
Back then,

234
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:52,040
when he acknowledged me
as his godfather,

235
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:55,080
he said that he admired
my martial arts skills.

236
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:59,520
The late emperor happened
to be disobedient,

237
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,560
so

238
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,840
I took him as my godson

239
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:08,120
and personally taught him martial arts.

240
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,400
You taught His Majesty martial arts?

241
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:13,880
I only taught him for three months.

242
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:16,840
I didn't expect him to be so gifted.

243
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,320
After three months,

244
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:22,080
it was like he trained for three years.

245
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,760
Later on, I stopped teaching him

246
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:27,880
and commanded people
to bring him hunting and having fun.

247
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,920
You only taught him for three months?

248
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,520
You got both of them.

249
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,600
Your Majesty, nice shot.

250
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,600
That's right.

251
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:00,360
After one year,

252
00:16:01,560 --> 00:16:04,360
his bow and arrow skill
surpassed everyone's.

253
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:05,760
After three years,

254
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:09,680
no one could defeat him
in the Shencai Army.

255
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:14,160
I don't want his martial arts skills
to be good.

256
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:19,080
That was why I told him to concoct pills
and enjoy himself.

257
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:21,040
That was when Cheng Xi

258
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,440
went to him.

259
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:25,240
Cheng Xi is great with the technique
of concocting pills?

260
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:32,840
That was how Cheng Xi and Cheng Huaizhi
became powerful.

261
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:36,920
It was all because of me.

262
00:16:38,760 --> 00:16:40,040
Come to think of it,

263
00:16:41,280 --> 00:16:42,640
after doing one step wrong,

264
00:16:43,880 --> 00:16:45,520
everything afterwards was wrong.

265
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:49,120
How are you planning

266
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:50,560
to deal with Qi Yan then?

267
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,680
Prince An has arrived!

268
00:17:03,680 --> 00:17:04,920
Greetings, Duke Chu.

269
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,599
Prince An!

270
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:27,520
Prince An.

271
00:17:28,520 --> 00:17:32,840
This cricket has a nice color.

272
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:38,040
You're knowledgeable about crickets,
Duke Chu?

273
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:42,920
Not only do I know it,

274
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,120
I know how to raise it.

275
00:17:47,560 --> 00:17:48,680
The trick

276
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,440
is "fighting".

277
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:07,160
Your Majesty.

278
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,480
They already went down the mountain

279
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,040
to find

280
00:18:09,040 --> 00:18:10,160
the preys you shot earlier.

